Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.49,0:00:07.19,Main,woman,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.14,0:00:10.12,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,Why did she have to glare at us like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.12,0:00:13.12,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,Just because we're going on a trip doesn't \Nmean we've done something wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.12,0:00:15.33,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,I think that's just her job.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.84,0:00:18.91,Main,girl,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, yeah! It was crazy!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.91,0:00:20.70,Main,girl,0000,0000,0000,,So? So? What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.99,0:00:26.67,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,A plane!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.99,0:00:30.85,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,Is this the plane we're taking?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.85,0:00:31.55,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,I think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.99,0:00:33.55,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,Will it really fly?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.90,0:00:37.63,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,I always dreamed about being a plane!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.63,0:00:38.43,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,Being a plane?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.43,0:00:40.93,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, being a plane!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.66,0:01:04.21,Show_Title,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(2280,1225)}A Place Further Than the Universe
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.99,0:02:26.50,Hashtags,sign,0000,0000,0000,,#ExtraLargeHelping #SexyPinUp #24Hours
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.99,0:02:26.50,Ep_Title,sign,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome to the Durian Show
