Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.00,0:02:28.87,sign_3549_18_Dear_Mom,sign,0000,0000,0000,,Dear Mom
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.00,0:02:28.87,sign_3549_19_Dear_Mom_Dear_Mo,sign,0000,0000,0000,,Dear Mom\NDear Mom
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.16,0:02:29.92,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.70,0:02:34.53,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,It means the plane has stabilized \Nand you can walk around.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.53,0:02:35.30,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.97,0:02:37.80,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so nervous...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.04,0:02:43.88,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't realize this was your \Nfirst time on a plane, Shirase!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.88,0:02:46.88,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,I watched my mother fly \Nout a number of times,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.88,0:02:48.52,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,but I've never been on one myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.88,0:02:50.99,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,I bet you've flown lots of \Ntimes, right, Yuzu-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.99,0:02:53.02,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,For work, certainly...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.19,0:02:55.77,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,How do I use this?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.97,0:02:57.53,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,Same question! Same question!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.53,0:02:59.48,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,It says "Games"...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.48,0:03:01.78,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,Um, you press this...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.23,0:03:04.45,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,Is this soba?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.45,0:03:07.82,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,Can I trade my celery for your sweet egg?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.82,0:03:09.04,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.62,0:03:11.54,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,Green tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.11,0:03:24.12,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,Right! Go right!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.12,0:03:25.30,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, stay on your side!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.48,0:03:33.06,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,Why? Why am I the only \None who didn't get any?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.44,0:03:34.77,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,Because you were asleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.20,0:03:40.19,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,Um, turn off this "data roaming" thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.21,0:03:48.70,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,Wake her up.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.87,0:03:50.20,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,Kimari-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.51,0:03:54.17,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe you slept through all that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.41,0:03:55.38,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,We're here?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.20,0:03:59.02,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! So much English!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.02,0:04:00.55,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,Of course there is.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.78,0:04:02.28,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,Which way do we go?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.28,0:04:05.05,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,We're taking the subway, \Nso we'll follow the MRT signs.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.37,0:04:08.11,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean, you forgot \Nto change your money?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.11,0:04:11.28,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,And to change all your money...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.28,0:04:13.32,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,we're leaving in two days, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.32,0:04:15.81,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,You need to tell me this stuff in advance!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.32,0:04:19.55,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,It's hot...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.90,0:04:20.94,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,It's summer!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.94,0:04:23.85,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,Well, we're right by the equator, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.85,0:04:26.40,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,Last time I came, I could \Nhave just died right then.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.40,0:04:28.09,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,Where's the merlion? The merlion!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.09,0:04:29.83,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,It's not here, clearly.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.92,0:04:32.33,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,What a strange building...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.81,0:04:35.83,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,Shirase-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.83,0:04:37.72,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,Discount please!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.72,0:04:39.13,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.13,0:04:40.78,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,We can shop later!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.12,0:04:47.68,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,Darn it. It took us forever \Njust to get to the hotel...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.68,0:04:49.00,Main,both,0000,0000,0000,,Did it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.00,0:04:50.93,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,Because you bought all that stuff!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.93,0:04:55.65,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,We only have one day before we have \Nto get on a plane to Fremantle.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.65,0:04:57.94,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,We need to be efficient...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.68,0:05:01.71,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,A double bed!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.71,0:05:03.20,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,One, two!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.20,0:05:05.69,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,First comes rock! Rock-paper-scissors!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.41,0:05:08.21,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.21,0:05:09.45,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.45,0:05:11.41,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,We're betting on who has to \Nsleep next to you, Kimari.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.82,0:05:15.51,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,Kimari-san, why don't you \Njust start out on the floor?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.51,0:05:17.60,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,You'll probably fall \Nsooner or later anyway...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.60,0:05:18.70,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.70,0:05:22.13,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,Because that's what you did during training!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.50,0:05:23.63,Flashback,kima,0000,0000,0000,,So cold...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.25,0:05:26.13,Flashback,kima,0000,0000,0000,,So warm...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.47,0:05:27.98,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,I don't remember at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.98,0:05:29.39,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,That's why it's a problem!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.89,0:05:34.77,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, let's put our valuables \Nin here before we head out!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.14,0:05:37.77,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,Japanese yen, plane ticket, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.28,0:05:40.02,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.65,0:05:41.62,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.62,0:05:43.28,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,N-Nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.90,0:05:48.03,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,We'll get ready in our rooms and \Nmeet in the lobby in 30 minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.10,0:06:06.14,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,I've seen that! It's a pool, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.14,0:06:07.93,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.11,0:06:09.43,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.29,0:06:21.43,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,There it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.32,0:06:29.00,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,It's so...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.00,0:06:31.78,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,It's not as disappointing as I expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.78,0:06:35.21,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! I'd heard it was more disappointing!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.21,0:06:37.53,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,Were you hoping for disappointment?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.47,0:06:39.62,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,Line up.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.88,0:06:43.88,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,We gotta pose! We gotta pose!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.88,0:06:45.75,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.36,0:06:50.90,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,What, exactly, is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.58,0:06:56.56,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,Is this really oolong tea?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.56,0:06:58.68,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,That's what it says.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.46,0:07:00.69,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,Miso ramen?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.18,0:07:03.67,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,I told you, they won't have any.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.67,0:07:05.19,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,But it's ramen!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.19,0:07:06.57,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,Because of the miso.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.75,0:07:11.20,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,It's so...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.55,0:07:13.70,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,There must be some mistake...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.93,0:07:25.80,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,Stuffed to bursting.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.44,0:07:30.13,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,Shirase-san, your mouth's hanging open.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.62,0:07:35.14,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,Look what I bought!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.36,0:07:36.89,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,Durian ice cream!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.89,0:07:39.86,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,How do you even have room?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.49,0:07:41.92,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,It's dessert!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.92,0:07:43.27,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,Join me, Hinata-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.42,0:07:48.11,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,You want me to eat that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.11,0:07:50.81,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? Shirase-chan, then!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.74,0:07:52.86,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.50,0:07:59.57,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.53,0:08:07.24,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,I warned you...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.85,0:08:08.94,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Yuzu?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.94,0:08:09.51,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.91,0:08:13.01,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,You took out your passport when \Nwe went through customs, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.37,0:08:15.39,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,Well... yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.76,0:08:17.45,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,You still have yours, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.89,0:08:20.10,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,Of course. It's right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.06,0:08:22.22,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,Of course it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.68,0:08:30.36,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.78,0:08:31.96,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,Where's the pool?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.96,0:08:35.70,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,It's over there, but you can't \Ngo in unless you're a guest.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.70,0:08:37.33,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,What? Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.95,0:08:41.05,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,It's just an ordinary pool.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.05,0:08:42.50,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,Though it does have a nice view...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.50,0:08:44.83,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,No way! You've been in it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.83,0:08:46.79,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,Once, for a shoot...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.79,0:08:50.37,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, w-was it a sexy bikini pin-up?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.37,0:08:51.63,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,Are you making fun of me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.63,0:08:52.53,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,Was it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.53,0:08:53.88,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.15,0:09:03.85,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,It's a bit like the crossroads \Nof the sea, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.85,0:09:05.87,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,Is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.87,0:09:09.36,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,Then people leave here to \Ngo all over the world, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.39,0:09:11.38,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,Probably.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.64,0:09:19.07,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,It's kind of amazing, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.07,0:09:20.31,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,What is?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.31,0:09:24.50,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,In two days, we're leaving here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.50,0:09:27.12,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,But this view will remain the same, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.12,0:09:28.55,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,Of course it will.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.55,0:09:32.67,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,We'll go to Antarctica, \Nand come back to Japan,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.67,0:09:35.27,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,but boats will still come here every day,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.27,0:09:37.89,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,and the city will be full of people...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.18,0:09:42.83,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,Going to school, working their jobs, \Nhanging out with their friends...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.19,0:09:47.46,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,They'll all keep living their lives...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.80,0:09:50.21,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,It's the same in Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.85,0:09:53.30,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,School's still being held.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.30,0:09:55.42,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,They're probably having \Ndinner right about now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.01,0:10:01.78,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,In places we've never seen, \Nlocations we've never been...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.78,0:10:04.62,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,So many people are living \Nso many kinds of lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.42,0:10:08.09,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,Every day, without stopping.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.57,0:10:09.92,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,That's amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.43,0:10:12.92,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,Even though it's common sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.92,0:10:15.63,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,But I know what you're getting at.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.86,0:10:19.96,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,Hinata-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.96,0:10:20.51,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.25,0:10:23.14,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,You're hiding something, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.20,0:10:26.02,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,You're {\i1}hiding something{\i}, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.23,0:10:46.34,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,You can't find it anywhere?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.34,0:10:50.43,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,Well... I'm sure it'll turn up.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.43,0:10:51.67,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,It's so important, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.13,0:10:55.87,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,But then it would have come up \Nafter all this searching, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.87,0:10:57.67,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,That's true...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.93,0:11:00.67,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,Without a passport, not only \Ncan you not leave the country,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.67,0:11:02.48,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,you can't go back to Japan, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.48,0:11:04.12,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.12,0:11:07.43,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,Then, if it doesn't turn up...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.89,0:11:13.36,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! Long ago, I did live in Japan!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.36,0:11:15.61,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, the good old days!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.89,0:11:16.99,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,...is how it'll be.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.99,0:11:19.36,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,Why would I still work in a \Nconvenience store over here?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.79,0:11:22.07,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,Our flight's in two days!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.07,0:11:23.52,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry, don't worry!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.52,0:11:25.78,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,We'll work it out somehow. Somehow!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.78,0:11:27.06,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,How?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.39,0:11:28.96,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,Somehow!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.96,0:11:31.20,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, there're lots of options...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.20,0:11:32.25,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What{\i0} options?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.98,0:11:36.55,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,Options... like...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.55,0:11:37.50,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,Right back atcha!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.54,0:11:40.37,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.46,0:11:43.26,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, let's look it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.07,0:11:48.24,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,If you lose your passport,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.24,0:11:50.51,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,you can get a new one printed at the embassy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.51,0:11:53.33,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,The shortest time is... half a day.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.33,0:11:55.27,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,Then if we go tomorrow, \Nwe'll make it in time!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.56,0:11:58.89,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,But the embassy takes \NSundays and holidays off.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.89,0:12:00.29,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,And tomorrow is...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.29,0:12:01.32,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,Sunday.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.57,0:12:05.01,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.01,0:12:06.62,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,We convenience store clerks
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.62,0:12:10.65,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,work 24 hours a day, \N365 days a year, without rest!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.65,0:12:12.34,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,The government is stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.34,0:12:16.30,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,We'll just have to wait for a \Nplane two or three days later.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.30,0:12:19.71,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,We'll arrive later, but we'll \Nmake it before the boat leaves.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.06,0:12:21.11,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,Good idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.11,0:12:23.97,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,Tomorrow, let's stop by the airport counter.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.97,0:12:27.31,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,Are we going... to change our arrival date?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.16,0:12:30.76,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,It may be the only option.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.76,0:12:32.34,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,Will that be okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.34,0:12:36.60,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,I mean... the members of the expedition \Nare awfully strict about rules.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.28,0:12:39.96,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,They might say "maybe you shouldn't come."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.96,0:12:41.21,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.21,0:12:42.74,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,Extenuating circumstances and all that...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.74,0:12:43.89,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.34,0:12:45.52,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.52,0:12:48.55,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't we email Kanae-san about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.55,0:12:50.19,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,You mean, to tell her we'll be late?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.19,0:12:51.94,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,It seems like the best thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.96,0:12:58.53,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,Hey... look, we depart in the \Nmorning in two days, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.53,0:13:00.02,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,So we have a whole day to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.02,0:13:01.85,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,Let's talk again tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.85,0:13:04.22,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,After all, it might still turn up.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.51,0:13:05.60,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.80,0:13:08.30,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,Please, turn up!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.62,0:13:33.93,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,Merlion...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.58,0:13:34.41,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,I will murder you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.26,0:13:42.17,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,Either way, you three should \Nhead for Australia in two days.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.76,0:13:46.55,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,I think I can work this out on my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.55,0:13:48.05,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,So if I make it in time, I'll come after you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.49,0:13:50.18,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,And if you don't make it in time?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.63,0:13:52.81,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,I just go back to Japan, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.04,0:13:54.68,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,I can pay my own fare.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.65,0:14:00.72,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,I'll tell Kimari and the others myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.53,0:14:03.07,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.94,0:14:06.57,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,It's because I didn't want \Nto change flights, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.32,0:14:10.24,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,I'm well aware...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.24,0:14:14.08,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,that when things don't go the way \NI plan, I tend to get very annoyed.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.79,0:14:17.00,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you don't have to apologize, Shirase.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.00,0:14:19.26,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the one who lost my passport.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.26,0:14:21.33,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the one who should apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.83,0:14:22.96,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.42,0:14:24.65,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,That's not what this is!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.65,0:14:26.44,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,Sure it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.77,0:14:36.00,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to be a drag on you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.00,0:14:40.45,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,What if you're right, and you don't get \Nto go to Antarctica because of this?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.45,0:14:41.81,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,You'd never recover.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.81,0:14:42.86,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.27,0:14:45.65,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,I never said I wasn't going.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.65,0:14:48.36,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,You three go first. I'll catch up.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.74,0:14:49.41,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.00,0:14:52.06,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,Now it's settled!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.26,0:14:57.47,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,Let's all go together!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.47,0:15:01.13,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,I just have to email Kanae-san \Nand explain the situation...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.84,0:15:04.00,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,I would like to take a shower!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.06,0:15:07.22,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,Do you mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.47,0:15:28.35,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.53,0:15:33.00,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,Shirase, I know you were \Ntrying to be considerate.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.00,0:15:36.11,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,I just really hate that kind of thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.71,0:15:41.10,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,I know that's how relationships work, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.10,0:15:43.71,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,when people try to be considerate of me...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.13,0:15:46.87,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,it's disconcerting, I guess...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.87,0:15:50.22,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,Like I can't tell how they \Nreally feel anymore...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.70,0:15:53.83,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I couldn't handle high school,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.83,0:15:56.35,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,and wanted to be alone as much as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.23,0:16:01.94,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,At the end of the day, \Nwhen I'm with someone else,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.94,0:16:04.62,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,things usually end up like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.62,0:16:06.81,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,So, no need to worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.81,0:16:09.18,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,The problem's all on me...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.47,0:16:11.77,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,That's not true.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.77,0:16:13.20,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,I have problems, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.50,0:16:16.98,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,Ever since I came to high school, I've had \Nthis "keep away" aura running full blast.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.98,0:16:18.41,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,I've never been good around people—
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.41,0:16:20.21,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,This is what I'm talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.97,0:16:23.84,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,I told you, I don't like people \Nbeing considerate of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.56,0:16:25.76,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.76,0:16:27.04,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.04,0:16:31.37,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,Shirase, you want to go to Antarctica \Nmore than anyone, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.37,0:16:32.20,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.59,0:16:34.49,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,You've wanted to go forever, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.56,0:16:37.81,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,So what?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.60,0:16:41.14,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay to make that your priority!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.14,0:16:44.31,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,That's what would make me feel best.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.64,0:16:48.61,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.79,0:16:51.86,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,Good night.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.15,0:17:03.07,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,My alarm clock!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.99,0:17:17.13,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,She's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.13,0:17:19.18,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,Hinata-chan, over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.06,0:17:24.73,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you leave without me?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.13,0:17:27.78,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you were sleeping in \Nbecause you were under the weather!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.98,0:17:33.44,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,Yuzuki-chan's asking if we can \Nchange our tickets right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.59,0:17:40.49,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you don't have to worry about that now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.49,0:17:43.57,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,We decided that you three \Nwould go without me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.57,0:17:44.74,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,We did?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.74,0:17:46.21,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,That never happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.21,0:17:48.81,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, it did! Later on.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.81,0:17:50.53,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,Don't make things up.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.53,0:17:52.46,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you so stubborn?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.46,0:17:54.47,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,You're the one being stubborn!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.43,0:17:58.72,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,We can't do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.41,0:18:03.67,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,There's not another opening for \Nthese tickets for another month.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.67,0:18:05.07,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.07,0:18:07.65,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,It's because we bought the cheapest tickets.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.65,0:18:10.06,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,See? It can't be done.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.06,0:18:12.79,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,So you three should go tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.79,0:18:15.73,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,I'll get my passport reprinted myself, and—
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.60,0:18:17.70,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,Shirase-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.99,0:18:21.48,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,Change! Late two days! Air!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.48,0:18:22.58,Main,woman,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.29,0:18:28.58,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,Shirase-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.92,0:18:30.38,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,The mwillion yen...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.38,0:18:32.54,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,Please change! Four person!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.54,0:18:35.06,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! Why are you being so stubborn?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.06,0:18:36.09,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.09,0:18:37.58,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong with being stubborn?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.58,0:18:39.05,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,That's how I've always lived my life!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.05,0:18:42.19,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,I'm stubborn, people make fun of me, \Nand I've had awful experiences.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.19,0:18:44.06,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,But I remain stubborn...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.06,0:18:45.65,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,because I'm right!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.56,0:18:48.69,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't want me to be \Nconsiderate, I'll say it outright.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.95,0:18:50.98,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to be the kind of idiot \Nwho doesn't worry about something
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.98,0:18:52.31,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,just because you say "don't worry about it!"
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.31,0:18:54.91,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want the kind of shallow \Nrelationship where I go without you
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.91,0:18:56.07,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,because you say "just go without me!"
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.23,0:18:58.89,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to be the kind of \Ncoward who gives up without trying,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.89,0:19:00.45,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,even though we said we'd all go together!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.26,0:19:05.62,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,We're going, the four of us! \NAll four of us! That's my priority!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.22,0:19:09.52,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.30,0:19:19.72,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.98,0:19:24.99,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.99,0:19:26.12,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,Dunno...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.22,0:19:29.84,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,But it seems like a good thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.14,0:19:34.40,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,Is this... business class?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.78,0:19:37.57,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't have to go that far!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.57,0:19:39.90,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,There weren't any other openings. \NI didn't have a choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.44,0:19:42.34,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,Now I don't want you losing \Nthem, so hand them over.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.20,0:19:44.91,Main,hima,0000,0000,0000,,That's one million yen!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.29,0:19:49.29,Main,hima,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you acting so smug?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.60,0:19:51.72,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not acting smug.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.82,0:19:55.22,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,Well... maybe I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.85,0:19:59.30,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.51,0:20:01.96,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,You hate it when people act \Nconsiderate of you, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.96,0:20:03.78,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,So let's pretend I'm not.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.78,0:20:04.65,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, come on...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.65,0:20:07.56,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, we're all going together now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.73,0:20:10.31,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,So tomorrow, we'll go to the embassy and...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.47,0:20:17.73,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.69,0:20:26.99,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.25,0:20:33.44,Flashback,hina,0000,0000,0000,,My shoelace came untied.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.44,0:20:34.98,Flashback,hina,0000,0000,0000,,Hold this a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.33,0:20:37.82,Flashback,shira,0000,0000,0000,,It's dangerous to just carry it around.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.07,0:20:41.34,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,Hainanese chicken rice! \NHainanese chicken rice!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.58,0:20:45.04,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,Shirase-chan, I brought Hainanese \Nchicken rice and kaya toast!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.35,0:20:49.89,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,R-Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.89,0:20:51.02,Main,hian,0000,0000,0000,,Something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.02,0:20:52.40,Main,shi,0000,0000,0000,,N-Nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.40,0:20:55.23,Main,shi,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! Oh! Looks delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.16,0:20:57.36,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,Shirase-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.40,0:21:00.48,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,You're hiding something, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.58,0:21:04.36,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,You're {\i1}hiding something{\i}, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.08,0:21:10.87,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,Now, let's get eating!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.12,0:21:15.57,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,Shirase-chan and Hinata-chan's durian show!
